org.cojen.tupl.util

    org.cojen.tupl.util  
  • Classes in org.cojen.tupl.util used by org.cojen.tupl.util 
    Class and Description
    Clutch
    A clutch is a specialized latch which can support highly concurrent shared requests, under the assumption that exclusive requests are infrequent.
    Clutch.Pack
    Sharable object for supporting contended clutches.
    Latch
    Non-reentrant read-write latch, designed for throughout over fairness.
    Worker
    Simple task worker which has at most one background thread, and is expected to have only one thread enqueing tasks.
    Worker.Task
    One-shot worker task instance.
    WorkerGroup
    A group of workers for running tasks.
